<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="490">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zuo-ji-ke" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zuo-ji-ke" class="zg-link" title="左霁珂">左霁珂</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xiao-cao-cao-cao-cao" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xiao-cao-cao-cao-cao" class="zg-link" title="小草草草草">小草草草草</a></span>
